mod rt

// Cooperatively yield from the current green thread, returning control to
// the scheduler. The scheduler picks the next runnable task (or, in the
// single-task case, this same one) and resumes it. Lowers to wasm
// `suspend $yield_tag`; the scheduler's resume handler installs the
// matching `on $yield` clause.
@runtime("prim_rt_yield")
fn yield();
